@AstralVeil.Api_HostAddress = http://localhost:5020

### 健康检查
GET {{AstralVeil.Api_HostAddress}}/health
Accept: application/json

###

### OpenAPI（Development）
GET {{AstralVeil.Api_HostAddress}}/openapi/v1.json
Accept: application/json

###

### 运势（需配置 OPENAI_API_KEY，否则 503 NO_API_KEY）
POST {{AstralVeil.Api_HostAddress}}/api/horoscope
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "birthYear": 1999,
  "birthMonth": 11,
  "birthDay": 8,
  "zodiacLabel": "天蝎座",
  "dateISO": "2026-04-04"
}

